rows.label: qst101803_msg001
rows.name: LIST_QST101803の仮実装

rows.label: qst101803_msg002
rows.name: ジゾーはすでに死んでいる

rows.label: qst101803_msg0001
rows.name: Possah! Budada safe home!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0002
rows.name: Who you...?

rows.label: qst101803_msg0003
rows.name:
Budada! Maybe Possah not recognize,
because Budada lose weight?

rows.label: qst101803_msg0004
rows.name: Budada...?

rows.label: qst101803_msg0005
rows.name: Budada not in this world anymore.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0006
rows.name:
Budada set out for Badfella's Cave
Fort. Terrible place. Possah wait days
and days and days, but no Budada.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0007
rows.name:
But Budada back home now!
Look closely Budada's face!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0008
rows.name: Hmmmmm...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0009
rows.name:
Budada was roundy-fatty,
fluffy-puffy Nopon.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0010
rows.name:
Lanky-gangly, filthy-mucky Nopon
is not Budada!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0011
rows.name:
You nasty Nopon, playing nasty trick on
grieving Possah!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0012
rows.name: Wah...Waaaaah!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0013
rows.name:
Oooohhhhh... *sniff*
Budada OK now...probably...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0014
rows.name:
This all Budada's fault. Days of not
moving make Budada very thin.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0015
rows.name:
But if Budada bring Blade Vahsah,
Possah must understand.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0016
rows.name:
Budada and Possah and Vahsah often
together, very good buddies.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0017
rows.name: But Vahsah not here...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0018
rows.name: Where Vahsah go...?

rows.label: qst101803_msg0019
rows.name: Vahsah, Vahsah... Where are Vahsah?

rows.label: qst101803_msg0020
rows.name: Oh! Budada have idea!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0021
rows.name:
Must have gone to city!
To Fons Maim!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0022
rows.name:
Yes, Vahsah go there and search
people to help Budada!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0023
rows.name:
Vahsah... You hear Budada...?
It OK now... Budada is here, here...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0024
rows.name:
No good... Budada cannot reach
to Vahsah's silly mind.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0025
rows.name: Thank you, friends.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0026
rows.name:
Please escort Budada to Fons Maim
so can find Vahsah!
